  "keyFeatures": [
    "Remap hardware buttons (volume, side key, gamepad, keyboard, mouse, headset, fingerprint sensor)",
    "Create complex macros with over 100 available actions",
    "Flexible trigger types: long press, double press, multi-key combinations",
    "Constraints to control when key maps are active (app in foreground, screen state, Bluetooth device, time of day, etc.)",
    "On-screen floating button layouts to create virtual keys in any app",
    "Expert Mode via Shizuku for low-latency event injection without root",
    "Key map groups for organizing and batch-controlling mappings",
    "Backup and restore key maps",
    "Broadcast API for integration with other Android apps",
    "Bluetooth device-aware key mapping"
  ],
